hập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/%C3%94ng-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-7WbJ_ECEoM4o3vDKEslRfQ">Ông Sơn tự - 翁山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-KrhE9fPPdxg7MJNECyal4Q">Phạm Viết Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/S%E1%BA%A7u/poem-NVuu8A-bEa9v0vpXtuAibA">Sầu - 愁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/author-sRwDvUqTTXJgu1Qk5ewg6w">Vi Trang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Cung/S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh-ph%C3%B9ng-ti%E1%BB%81u-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-Q9wyAYj2hV2Q-5kwNQ7ChQ">Sơn hành phùng tiều giả - 山行逢樵者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Cung/author-cDUIMuAqZhyluXUiTPluKw">Hồ Trọng Cung</a>)<br></div>	</div>
